Package org.drasyl.util

Class Worm<T>

java.lang.Object
org.drasyl.util.Worm<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of the worm object
public class Worm<T> extends Object
This class wraps an object of type T and serves as a write once read many (worm) memory.
